      java.util.List<java.lang.String> Parser.parseItemDetails(WebLink webLink, java.lang.String[] webPagePrasingKey, java.lang.String[] productDescriptionPrasingKey)
      Parse the saved web page to extract items' details specified in parsing key - one item per web page.

      Parsing process divided in five steps: Step 1: extract cover url and all authors from web page -- webPagePrasingKey [0,3]. Step 2: find web page part with product details -- productDescriptionPrasingKey. Step 3: extract publication year and publisher from publication details -- keys [4,5]. Step 4: extract ISBN from product details -- webPagePrasingKey [6,7]. Step 5: extract Average Customer Review from publication details -- webPagePrasingKey [8,9], e.g.
